text:
When it comes to Australia's borders, the buck stops with the Commonwealth.

The #RubyPrincess has led to 700 coronavirus cases, over 20 tragic deaths and 10% of all cases in Australia.

Then there's the real, tragic, human consequences of this calamitous border failure. https://t.co/Xca5uLuLUx
